### Bluetooth
load-module module-bluetooth-policy
load-module module-bluetooth-discover

### CamillaDSP - write to ALSA Loopback playback side
### (module-udev-detect fails for Loopback because CamillaDSP holds capture side)
load-module module-alsa-sink device=hw:Loopback,0,0 sink_name=camilladsp_out format=s16le rate=48000 channels=2 tsched=0
set-default-sink camilladsp_out
